<TEXT>
if youre thinking of updating your bathroom youre among an 
estimated 7 percent of american households with similar plans 
a survey in late 1987 for the trade magazine kitchen and bath 
business indicated that between 52 million and 65 million baths 
would be remodeled during 1988 the 25000 consumers surveyed 
